videos.headline: McCrae powers in for goal-line TD vs. Cincinnati
videos.description: Greg McCrae takes the handoff up the middle and falls into the end zone for a 3-yard UCF touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (McCrae powers in for goal-line TD vs. Cincinnati) 2020/11/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Cincy muffed punt results in UCF touchdown
videos.description: Ryan Montgomery can't hold on to the punt as UCF recovers deep in Cincinnati territory, setting up a 6-yard touchdown catch by Marlon Williams.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Cincy muffed punt results in UCF touchdown) 2020/11/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ridder connects with Whyle for 29-yard TD
videos.description: Desmond Ridder slings a pass to Josh Whyle across the middle for a 29-yard Cincinnati touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ridder connects with Whyle for 29-yard TD) 2020/11/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gabriel finds Williams for 19-yard TD
videos.description: Dillon Gabriel throws to Marlon Williams for a 19-yard UCF touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Gabriel finds Williams for 19-yard TD) 2020/11/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ridder extends over the UCF line for touchdown
videos.description: Desmond Ridder extends the football over the goal line for a Cincinnati score, and his second rushing touchdown of the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Ridder extends over the UCF line for touchdown) 2020// ESHEET

videos.headline: Ridder leads Bearcats with 4 TDs to remain undefeated
videos.description: Desmond Ridder throws a pair of touchdowns and runs for two more in No. 7 Cincinnati's 36-33 win vs. UCF.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Ridder leads Bearcats with 4 TDs to remain undefeated) 2020/11/21 ESHEET SOTFULL
